title: 100% Chiropractic Austin Rosedale
description:
Dr. Annie Wood is the Clinic Director at 100% Chiropractic Austin Rosedale. 100% Chiropractic is a leader in corrective chiropractic care. While we help manage symptoms like back pain, what we really specialize in is bringing your spine back to its ideal curves addressing the root causes of dysfunction, allowing your nervous system to function at 100% and restoring your body's natural ability to heal.

Dr. Annie brings a decade of dedicated chiropractic expertise across Colorado and Texas to athletes, families, and individuals seeking optimal health. Since 2013, she has specialized in sports performance and family care, holding a Webster Certification and membership in the International Chiropractic Pediatric Association (ICPA). Her experience includes proven success with CrossFit athletes, golfers, and former dancers, helping them enhance performance and recover from injuries. Dr. Wood's comprehensive approach serves patients across all life stages - from supporting athletic achievement to ensuring healthy development in children and providing specialized care for expecting mothers. Her proven track record in multiple states reflects her commitment to delivering results through natural, evidence-based care.

We offer cutting edge chiropractic care, massage therapy, and a full line of supreme quality nutritional supplements. Our incredible doctors, assistants, and therapists care about our patients and their individual health goals; and work directly with our patients to make sure they turn those goals into a reality. We offer our patients include Corrective Care, Family Wellness, Personal Injury (Auto Accident), Prenatal, and Pediatric, as well as Massage Therapy. At 100% Chiropractic, we don’t just treat pain—we work to educate, inspire, empower, and provide lasting care for our patients to live their lives to their fullest potential.

We offer the chiropractic care families are wanting, and the legendary 100% customer service they deserve. We encourage everyone to truly live life at 100%!

title: Austin Ketamine Clinic
description:
Austin Ketamine Clinic in Austin, Texas, is a family-owned and operated clinic with a compassionate staff that honors the principles of dignity, respect, and free will. The team opened their own ketamine therapy clinic out of concern for people who struggle with mental health disorders but can’t find effective treatment with standard medical care.

The professionals at Austin Ketamine Clinic offer ketamine infusion therapy for the treatment of various mental health conditions. Research has shown that ketamine has the potential to rapidly balance brain chemicals to alleviate the symptoms of mental health disorders such as depression, anxiety, suicidal thoughts, bipolar disorder, obsessive-compulsive disorder (OCD), and post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD). In addition, ketamine infusion therapy has also shown efficacy for patients with Tourette syndrome and those who need help breaking an addiction to alcohol and drugs. The team at Austin Ketamine Clinic offers more than 100 years of cumulative experience, which they combine with a fierce dedication to establishing a trusting relationship that supports each person’s recovery.

When patients come to the clinic, they feel embraced by the staff and the peaceful environment. The location was specifically chosen to maximize the best "set and setting" possible.  The clinic backs up to Barton Creek Greenbelt, where patients are immersed in the sights and sounds of nature. The team purposefully created this environment to gently support each person’s health and wellness. 

Each patient has the personal attention of the team throughout their ketamine treatment, which goes beyond staying with patients during their therapy. The team stays in touch and monitors their mental health when they’re not in the clinic.

Ketamine therapy isn’t covered by most insurance companies, so the team at Austin Ketamine Clinic offers packages and works with you to help you afford the treatment you need, not wanting cost to impose a barrier to treatment.

To learn more about how ketamine can help treat conditions that don’t respond to conservative medical treatment or to discuss the costs, call the office or email admin@austinketamineclinic.com to schedule a complimentary consultation.

title: Dell Laser Consultants
description:
Dell Laser Consultants was established to provide absolute state-of-the-art care in the field of vision correction surgery. We realize that you only have one set of eyes, and they deserve the best. From the moment you walk in the door, it will be apparent to you that we take this responsibility seriously. With the very finest technology available, and a caring and professional staff, we are dedicated to surgical excellence.

Dr. Dell’s consulting relationships with a variety of ophthalmic companies allow us to offer many new technologies, often years before they are available elsewhere. Through these relationships, we are able to offer the widest technological array of different lasers and diagnostic equipment available anywhere in Austin.


Our laser treatment suites are equipped with highly sophisticated Liebert environmental control systems. These industrial systems are used in sensitive computer data centers and microchip clean rooms. They are used to precisely control the temperature, humidity and air filtration system in the laser suite.

The importance of this might not be immediately obvious until you learn that even small changes in the density of the air in the laser suite can affect the outcome of the procedure. You will not find anything resembling this level of technology in most laser centers.

The excimer and femtosecond lasers we use in laser vision correction are incredibly sensitive pieces of equipment. Each one consists of highly sensitive optics, precisely aligned mirrors, sophisticated electronics and computer control systems. Even the slightest movement of the laser requires a factory technician to completely recalibrate the device.

Schedule a consultation at Dell Laser Consultants for LASIK Surgery, Refractive Surgery, Dry Eye Treatment & Cataract Surgery in Austin and see for yourself why we believe we offer the finest care available anywhere.

description: Greater Austin Pain Center is a top-rated pain management clinic located in Austin, that’s known for providing lasting pain relief, backed by modern research and the latest medical techniques. Our team of pain management specialists, physicians, and board certified anesthesiologists know how to treat pain effectively and conservatively, and would love to help you recover fully! At Greater Austin Pain Center, will take a multidisciplinary approach to treating pain, and offer a wide range of treatment options depending on the type and severity of your condition. We can provide both minimally-invasive, non-surgical options, such as nerve blocks and steroid injections, as well as surgical options, should they be necessary. We regularly perform interventional procedures including but not limited to spinal cord stimulation, kyphoplasty, epidural steroid injection, radiofrequency ablation, nerve blocks, and joint injections, and often combine treatments with physical therapy, lifestyle modification, and medication for even better results. Finally, our team of pain management physicians keep up abreast of the latest research and developments in multidisciplinary pain management, and have the skills and experience to recommend a treatment plan designed specifically for you. During your initial appointment, we’ll conduct a thorough assessment of your medical history and recommend a custom treatment plan designed to help you fully recover.
